dc_title_s: Bridgeton from Water Street to South Avenue, and Cedar Dell Avenue to Glass Street
dc_description_s: Map covers the area of Bridgeton between Water Street and South Avenue and Cedar Dell Avenue and Glass Street. |Map shows the land granted by the State of New Jersey, the owners of the land, the Cohansey River, exterior bulkhead lines, and the MWH Line.
dct_spatial_sm: Grant by the State of New Jersey to The West Jersey Railroad Co. August 31, 1893
